column5: What's up all I'll be staying in minden for a couple days next week.  Going to be getting out ice fishing for sure.  I've already talked to a couple of operators on the area, both said the fishing has been pretty slow. Any suggestions on places or operators pm if you feel the need......thanks

Fishing sure wasn't good today..,  It looked alright on gull lake, theres a small town out there (about 15 huts). I don't know if they were catching, but you'll have good ice at least, about a foot. Good luck!
hi christopher k  where you at pine ridge?
Hi Christopher K,  what presentations did you try?
Thanks fellas I'll be there wednesday til friday a report to follow.
